    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. The assessment team concludes the model is fit for the stated context of use.",
